      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2 used under an ISO 9001-certified QMS; FDA in-house solver subject to annual verification suite; documented version control and change management procedures in place for all three ensemble members."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
