      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Nonlinear elastic-plastic titanium alloy constitutive model (isotropic hardening, Ramberg-Osgood) selected based on literature evidence; contact interactions at screw-rod and rod-block interfaces modelled with penalty formulation validated against coupon tests."
    },
    {
