      "rationale": "Material properties derived from lot-specific tensile coupon testing (n=5 per lot); geometric inputs from coordinate measuring machine data; friction coefficient characterised by dedicated tribology study (μ=0.22 ± 0.03)."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
