      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single ASTM F1717 configuration (L4-L5 two-level construct, 50 mm spacer block). Variation across loading rates, spacer heights, or multi-level configurations was not explored. This factor is one gradation below required level; risk accepted given conservative single-condition selection per regulatory precedent."
