      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Direct mapping between experimental setup parameters and FEA boundary conditions documented in simulation plan; torque preload on set-screw replicated via pretension element; displacement-controlled loading rate matched to crosshead speed."
