      "rationale": "Construct stiffness and peak failure load compared using normalised error metric; mean absolute error 4.1% for stiffness, 6.3% for failure load; all predictions within experimental 95% confidence intervals."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the quantities of interest",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
